Report.Name: Tổng hợp vật tư nhập theo KH-Import-By Maker

DataSource.RecordSource:
Select Year,Month,PartNo,Model,PartName,Category,Type,VendorCode,VendorName,
MakerCode,MakerName,Sum(Isnull(Quantity,0))as Quantity,
Sum(Isnull(TotalCIF,0))as TotalCIF,Sum(Isnull(TotalInland,0))AS TotalInland,
Sum(Isnull(CIPAmount,0))as CIPAmount,Sum(Isnull(ImportTaxAmount,0))ImportTaxAmount,
Sum(Isnull(OrtherAmount,0))OrtherAmount,UM from v_POReceiptImport
Group by Year,Month,MakerCode,VendorCode,PartNo,PartName,Model,Category,Type,
VendorName,MakerName,UM

Field.Name: fldTitle
Field.Text: TONG HOP VAT TU NHAP THEO KE HOACH-IMPORT-BY MAKER
